            <div class="tier-bottom">Get it →</div>
          </a>
          <a href="/products/jockshock/" class="tier">
            <div class="tier-label">6-Pack</div>
            <div class="tier-detail">6 × 32oz</div>
            <div class="tier-price">$99.99</div>
            <div class="tier-bottom">Get it →</div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- RELATED -->
    <section class="related">
      <div class="related-inner">
        <p class="section-eyebrow">Related</p>
        <h2 class="section-headline">More from the gear bag.</h2>
        <div class="related-grid">
          <a href="/learn/shoe-deodorizer-spray/" class="related-card">
            <h3>Shoe deodorizer spray</h3>
            <p>The cleats, the training shoes, the kid's sneakers. Same routine, different gear.</p>
          </a>
          <a href="/learn/get-smell-out-of-cleats/" class="related-card">
            <h3>Get the smell out of cleats</h3>
            <p>Soccer, football, lacrosse, baseball. The cross-sport cleat playbook.</p>
          </a>
          <a href="/learn/how-to-mold-a-mouthguard/" class="related-card">
            <h3>How to mold a mouthguard</h3>
            <p>The pre-fitting parent guide. Boil-and-bite, custom fit, what the kid needs.</p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

